211
00:22:47,589 --> 00:22:50,010
I understand his power.

212
00:22:50,084 --> 00:22:55,022
To him, I may only be a frivolous coward..

213
00:22:56,414 --> 00:23:01,086
But what.. what is this feeling that's gushing out of me?

214
00:23:01,154 --> 00:23:05,433
I don't know.. I don't know, but I..

215
00:23:05,750 --> 00:23:09,168
..don't want to lose to this guy even if I die!

